metadata.name: WHO AM I
metadata.description:
Bye andyhsu.eth  
Hello 0xAndy.eth

Not easy decision to change my long-used web3 name.

Inspired by my 7-year-old girl's work "WHO AM I", I just put it up as free OE to memorize this moment.

No utility, no nothing, but if >69 minted, a raffle for the OE work by one of my beloved artist Zipcy.  
https://opensea.io/collection/sn-legends-of-the-digital-age
